msgid "[[!meta title=\"About our website being offline last week-end\"]]\n"
msgstr ""
"[[!meta title=\"Sobre el nostre lloc web fora de línia el cap de setmana "
"passat\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta date=\"Wed, 05 May 2021 15:00:00 +0000\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta date=\"Wed, 05 May 2021 15:00:00 +0000\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"As many of you noticed, our main server was offline from Friday April 30 "
"19:09 UTC until Monday May 3 05:58 UTC."
msgstr ""
"Com molts de vosaltres heu notat, el nostre servidor principal va estar fora "
"de línia des del divendres 30 d'abril a les 19:09 UTC fins al dilluns 3 de "
"maig a les 05:58 UTC."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This was caused by a hardware failure in one of the many Power Distribution "
"Units on the rack where our main server is hosted. Riseup, also hosted in "
"the same datacenter, suffered from the [same hardware failure](https://"
"twitter.com/riseupnet/status/1388214079316283394)."
msgstr ""
"Això va ser degut a una fallada de maquinari en una de les moltes unitats de "
"distribució d'energia del bastidor on està allotjat el nostre servidor "
"principal. Riseup, també allotjat al mateix centre de dades, va patir la ["
"mateixa fallada de maquinari](https://twitter.com/riseupnet/status/"
"1388214079316283394)."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, the outage impacted all Tails users: upgrades were failing "
"and our website was not appearing when starting Tor Browser."
msgstr ""
"Malauradament, la interrupció va afectar tots els usuaris de Tails: les "
"actualitzacions fallaven i el nostre lloc web no apareixia en iniciar el "
"Navegador Tor."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Some of you were afraid that the Tails infrastructure could have gone under "
"an attack of some sort. This does not seem to have been the case. The actual "
"reasons for the power glitch are still being investigated, but all indicates "
"that it was a simple hardware failure. There are no signs of malicious "
"activity whatsoever."
msgstr ""
"Alguns de vosaltres teníeu por que la infraestructura de Tails pogués haver "
"patit algun atac. No sembla que hagi estat així. Encara s'estan investigant "
"els motius reals de la fallada d'alimentació, però tot indica que es va "
"tractar d'una simple fallada de maquinari. No hi ha cap indici d'activitat "
"maliciosa."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"It took us so much time to bring it back online because of a bad "
"configuration of our notification system. Our sysadmins only learned about "
"the outage when coming back to work on Monday."
msgstr ""
"Vam trigar molt de temps a tornar-lo a connectar a causa d'una mala "
"configuració del nostre sistema de notificacions. Els nostres administradors "
"de sistemes només es van assabentar de la interrupció quan van tornar a "
"treballar dilluns."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To avoid such long delay in the future, we will make our notification system "
"more resilient."
msgstr ""
"Per evitar un retard tan llarg en el futur, farem que el nostre sistema de "
"notificacions sigui més resistent."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Sorry for the inconvenience!"
msgstr "Disculpeu les molèsties!"
